# Vulnify runtime data
# Full live feeds are fetched on demand by the live ingest engine; never commit
# them (they are hundreds of MB). The real bundled subset in data/bundled/ is
# tracked so the platform works offline the moment it is cloned.
data/feeds/
data/config/
output/
*.part

